Note, I have recompiled this map to jb_carceris_final due the fact I missed a few spots. Now it's supposed to function 100%. 
============================================================================================================================

Here is my last version of my map **Jb_carceris**

**bz2zipped version**

Bz2 version will be avaible soon [here](http://www.gamemaps.nl/versluis/cstrike/maps/jb_carceris.bsp.bz2 "Bz2 Link")

**Some background information:**

- Skybox used; miltia 
- Brushesides used: 509928 (97.3%/100%)
- Brushes used: 75108 (76.4%/100%)
- Entdata: 409398 (104.1%/100%) (but it's stable enough)
- Custom resources: 150+


**In this map there can be found:**

- Soccer
 - Airball 
 - Anti Gravity
 - Dodgeball
 - Big ball
 - Regular soccer
- Disco
- Pool
 - Waterpolo
 - Diving **(updated)**
 - Jump rope
- LR
 - Gun Toss
 - Arena
 - Shot 4 Shot
 - Camp area **(new)**
- Yard one
 - Hot Potato
 - 4 in a row
 - Jumping contest
 - Pacman 
- Yard two
 - Simon says
 - Race
 - Minigolf (**new)**
 - Volleyball **(new)**


Changelog:

- Updated Pacman
- Upgraded a few more secrets
- re-balanced some secrets
- Added Minigolf
- Added Volleyball
- Updated Race (which wasn't playable)
- Updated the lightning


The map itself is fully optimized, and not heavy for any server at all.

For any suggestions or feedback, please reply!
